OL,3,CWife of imprisoned Chinese artist says
OL,4,Che will fight for freedom of expression
OL,6,FThe wife of a Chinese artist who has
OL,7,Fbeen held by police for more than a
OL,8,Fyear says her husband will stand up
OL,9,Ffor freedom of expression and not
OL,10,Faccept his artwork was a crime.
OL,12,FGao Zhen was arrested on August 26
OL,13,Flast year for historic art he had
OL,14,Fpreviously created with his brother,
OL,15,Fdepicting Mao and criticising the
OL,16,FCultural Revolution.
