OL,3,CWife of imprisoned Chinese artist says
OL,4,Che will fight for freedom of expression
OL,6,FThe 69-year-old has been living in the
OL,7,FUS since 2022 and had travelled back
OL,8,Fto China to visit a sick relative.
OL,9,FJust days into the family visit, his
OL,10,Fart studio was raided and several
OL,11,Fpieces of art were confiscated by
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,FGao is being held on the charge of
OL,15,Fsmearing China's heroes and martyrs, a
OL,16,Fcrime introduced in 2021 with a jail
OL,17,Fsentence of up to three years. His
OL,18,Fwife Yaliang Zhao, and seven-year-old
OL,19,Fson have been prevented from leaving
OL,20,FChina and returning to their home in
OL,21,Fthe US.
