OL,6,FGao's son is an American citizen and
OL,7,Fhas missed a year of schooling due to
OL,8,Fhis father's detention. Both Gao and
OL,9,Fhis wife are green card holders.
OL,11,FYaliang Zhao told me the last year has
OL,12,Fbeen extremely upsetting; she has only
OL,13,Fbeen allowed intermittent contact with
OL,14,Fher husband, and her son needs his
OL,15,Ffather back.
