OL,3,CWife of imprisoned Chinese artist says
OL,4,Che will fight for freedom of expression
OL,6,FIn 2016, I met Gao Zhen and his
OL,7,Fbrother Gao Qiang, collectively known
OL,8,Fas the Gao Brothers, at their studio
OL,9,Fin 798, a famous art district in
OL,10,FBeijing. We were reporting on the
OL,11,FCultural Revolution, and they showed
OL,12,Fus their exhibit depicting a firing
OL,13,Fsquad of Mao's with their rifles
OL,14,Ftrained on Jesus.
OL,16,FThat was one of the most famous of
OL,17,Ftheir many exhibits characterising
OL,18,FChina's former Communist Party leader
OL,19,Fwho launched the two-decade-long
OL,20,FCultural Revolution in the 1960s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
