OL,3,CWife of imprisoned Chinese artist says
OL,4,Che will fight for freedom of expression
OL,6,FAll of the Gao Brothers' works predate
OL,7,Fthe 2021 law against insulting China's
OL,8,Fheroes and martyrs, and although Gao
OL,9,Fknew about the new law when he
OL,10,Freturned to China last year, he didn't
OL,11,Fbelieve he was at risk, because his
OL,12,Fcontroversial artworks were more than
OL,13,Ften years old.
OL,15,FMuch of Gao Brothers' work has been
OL,16,Finspired by their father, who was
OL,17,Fimprisoned during the Cultural
OL,18,FRevolution. They have never accepted
OL,19,Fthe authorities' claim that he took
OL,20,Fhis own life in jail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
