OL,3,CWife of imprisoned Chinese artist says
OL,4,Che will fight for freedom of expression
OL,6,FIt is thought he is one of the only
OL,7,Fpeople to be charged retrospectively
OL,8,Funder the crime of slandering heroes
OL,9,Fand martyrs.
OL,11,FIn the past decade, under the
OL,12,Fleadership of President Xi Jinping,
OL,13,Flawyers, artists, activists and
OL,14,Fjournalists have been routinely
OL,15,Ftargeted under similar "slander''
OL,16,Flaws, in particular the vague crime of
OL,17,F"picking quarrels".
